Ear1-orc fang earing<br>
Ear2-orc fang earing<br>
Neck-7str 7int Necklace<br>
Face-Dented Brass Mask<br>
Head-Helm of Ro<br>
Ring 1-6ac 65hp ring<br>
Ring2- 75hp -10magic ring<br>
Bracer1-Bronze Bracer<br>
Bracer2-Bronze Bracer<br>
Hands- Gaunts of Ro<br>
Arms - Rygorr Arms<br>
Boots- Crustacean Shell Boots<br>
Legs- Greaves of Ro<br>
Chest- Breastplate of Ro<br>
Belt - Bronze Girdle<br>
Back - Lizard Scale Cloak<br>
Shoulder- empty<br>
1hs-Sporali's Defender Blade<br>
Sheild-Cracked Darkwood sheild / Round Velium (if i go encumbered)<br>
2hs - Nathsar Greatsword<br>
2hb - Silver etched warhammer<br>
2hp- centi-warspear 20/30 5ac, str, stam<br>
1hb- none yet<br>
And an EEbag to carry all this crap around.<br>
<br>
Can you please tell me what to sell/buy to improve myself?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uwhitchywhon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Whitchywhon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/12/01 7:24:22 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My Twink Paladin Equip...Need Help</span><hr size=1> From what I've heard<br>
<br>
Get rid of the + int/str neck and get something with AC<br>
<br>
Also change the +75hp ring for another 6ac +65hp ring.<br>
<br>
At least get some bronze for your shoulders while your looking for something better.<br>
<br>
All above statements are IMHO<br>
<br>
I was once told &quot;AC is king, then HP for a Paly&quot;.<br>
<br>
Good luck<br>
<br>
Chipp Lvl. 21 Paly<br>
 25 sshaman<br>
 23 Ranger<br>
 51 Necro<br>
  4 Monk<br>
  7 Warrior <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugilfalas.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gilfalas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(12/12/01 9:09:36 am)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: My Twink Paladin Equip...Need Help</span><hr size=1> Ears are fine<br>
<br>
Neck-Get anything but a Str/Int No AC item. Get Bronze or a chipped Veilium Amulet or fine steel if you can. Paladins use AC to tank and WISDOM for their mana. The Necklace you have does nothing for you exept make you get hit more and add to your carrying capacity.<br>
<br>
Face, Head, Ring 1: All fine<br>
Ring2- Good till you can get another AC 6 +65 HP ring.<br>
<br>
Bracers, Hands, Arms, Boots, Legs, Chest: all fine<br>
<br>
Belt - Dump the bronze and get a Strawspun belt. 10AC and weight 6. Usually 50 plat. at most these days.<br>
<br>
Back - is fine<br>
<br>
Shoulder- Try for Crested Spaulders or Adamantite Epolets. Can usually get VERY cheap these days.<br>
<br>
All the rest is absolutely fine for a level 1. As you level and learn you will be able to upgrade.<br>
<br>
The gear you list was what I was wearing at level 40 for the most part. So you should be just fine. <p><center>
